    "While we notice a relative inversion between far-right leaders such as Nicolas Dupont Aignan and Eric Zemmour, the overall arena is similar.",
    "All in all, the general accuracy is equivalent between the different variants, 85% of the predictions off by less than 0.1 (Figure 14), more than 60% of the prediction offs by less than 25% for large displacement ∆ op > 0.05 (Figure 16).",
